quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  8,20,"Enywe abasuubila! Murie Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe, mulamwilukha tawe nimuwulilanga"
  8,21,Ne mulaba shinga balia baboolanga mbu; “Khuwulile” nekhane bashili okhuwulila
  8,22,"Toto tsisolo tsimbi muno imbeli wa Nyasaye- nitsilia tsikholanga mbu shitsiwulilanga tawe- nitsindimbe, tsisilu. Tsilia tsilekhonyela obwongo tawe"
  8,23,Ne Nyasaye alolanga obulayi bwosi bwosi mubo yakha bawulilisiye nekata abawulilisia bakhakalukhane butswa
  8,24,"Enywe abasuubila mufuchilile omulango kwa Nyasaye nende Omurumwa olwa abalanga mukalia aketsa okhubahelesia obulamu, amalayi, ne manye mbu Nyasaye yenjilanga hakari womundu nende omwoyo kukwe, ne ewuwe ni amulikhung’asibwa"
  8,25,"Ne murie eshinyasio eshilakhaya okhunyoola balia bakhola obubii bonyene mwinywe, ne mumanye mbu Nyasaye ni omululu weshinyasio"
  8,26,"Ne yitsulile, olwa mwali batiti, olwa mwalolekhananga abateshele khushialo, olwa mwaritsanga Abandu okhubayula, mana nabahelesia habundu alayi okhwikhala, mana nabahelesia amani khubuhabini bubwe, ne nabahelesia omukabo omulayi khomunyoole okhupa orio"
  8,27,"Enywe abasuubila, mulakholela Nyasaye nende Omurumwa obulianga tawe. Ne mulakhola obulianga khukhusuubilana khwenyu tawe- nimumanyile"
  8,28,Ne manye mbu emiandu chienyu nende abana benyu ni amatemo. Ne toto Nyasaye ali nende omurungo omukhongo